<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-header__title">About Us</h1>
        <p class="page-header__breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / About Us</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Academy Intro -->
    <section class="section" aria-label="About the Academy">
      <div class="container about-content">
        <span class="section__label">Est. 2012</span>
        <h2>About the Academy</h2>
        <p>Taleem Ul Quran Online Quran Academy is a distinguished institution founded in 2012 by Maulana Umar Qayoom, a renowned Islamic scholar. Initially established as a physical academy with centers in the UAE and Pakistan, we have since transitioned to an online platform to extend our reach and provide high-quality Quranic education worldwide.</p>
        <p>Our academy is dedicated to providing high-quality Quranic education exclusively tailored for males, females, and children. Certified female Almiah, Hafizah, and Qariah Quran teachers guide and nurture the learning journey of our students. While we prioritize empowering mothers, sisters, daughters, and children in their pursuit of Quranic knowledge, we also extend our services to boys with parental consent.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section class="section section--alt" aria-label="Why Choose Us">
      <div class="container about-content">
        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>At Taleem Ul Quran Online Quran Academy, we stand out for our:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Desired Timing — learn on your schedule</li>
          <li>Experienced and certified instructors</li>
          <li>Dedicated female teachers for female students</li>
          <li>Interactive and engaging online classes</li>
          <li>Flexible learning schedules</li>
          <li>Individual one-on-one sessions</li>
          <li>Supportive and nurturing environment</li>
          <li>Affordable fees with family discounts</li>
          <li>Multi-language support</li>
          <li>Access from any device, anywhere</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CEO's Message -->
    <section class="section" aria-label="CEO's Message">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
          <span class="section__label">Leadership</span>
          <h2 class="section__title">CEO's Message</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="ceo-section fade-in">
          <div class="ceo__photo">
            <img src="/images/pics/ceo-image.png" alt="Maulana Umar Qayoom — CEO, Taleem Ul Quran" width="220" height="220" loading="lazy">
            <p class="ceo__name">Maulana Umar Qayoom</p>
            <p class="ceo__role">CEO, Taleem Ul Quran Academy</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ceo__message">
            <h2>Assalamu Alaikum wa Rahmatullahi wa Barakatuh</h2>
            <p>I am Maulana Umar Qayoom, the CEO of Taleem Ul Quran Online Quran Academy. With a background in Quranic studies and years of experience serving as an IMAM and KHATEEB in AWQAF UAE, I am honored to lead our academy in its mission to spread the teachings of the Quran far and wide.</p>
            <p>Our commitment to excellence, combined with our dedication to providing a nurturing learning environment, sets us apart as a premier destination for Quranic education. Through our comprehensive curriculum, meticulously curated resources, and dedicated faculty of scholars and educators, we strive to empower our students to become confident and informed ambassadors of the Quran.</p>
            <p>As we continue on this noble endeavor, I am filled with gratitude for the unwavering support of our students, faculty, and community partners. Together, we embark on a journey of discovery, guided by the light of knowledge and the blessings of Allah.</p>
            <p><strong>Fi Amanillah,</strong><br>Maulana Umar Qayoom<br><em>CEO, Taleem Ul Quran Online Quran Academy</em></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Teaching Methodology -->
    <section class="section section--alt" aria-label="Teaching Methodology">
      <div class="container about-content">
        <h2>Our Teaching Methodology</h2>
        <p>We employ cutting-edge online platforms like Zoom, Google Meet, and MS Teams to facilitate dynamic and immersive Quranic learning experiences. Our teaching philosophy prioritizes student engagement, fostering an environment where interactive participation is encouraged and valued.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Comprehensive Quranic curriculum</li>
          <li>Individualized attention to each student</li>
          <li>Regular assessments and feedback</li>
          <li>Accessible learning resources and materials</li>
          <li>Interactive and engaging learning activities</li>
          <li>Integration of multimedia resources</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission & Vision -->
    <section class="section" aria-label="Mission and Vision">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
          <span class="section__label">Our Purpose</span>
          <h2 class="section__title">Mission & Vision</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="mv-grid fade-in">
          <div class="mv-card">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To provide accessible, high-quality Quranic education worldwide, nurturing spiritual growth and fostering a deeper connection to Allah. Through our comprehensive curriculum and dedicated faculty, we empower students to confidently engage with the complexities of the Quran, embodying its teachings in their daily lives.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mv-card">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>To be a global leader in Quranic education, recognized for our commitment to excellence, innovation, and inclusivity. We aspire to cultivate a community of lifelong learners dedicated to knowledge, spirituality, and personal growth, guided by the timeless wisdom of the Quran.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
